name: Two Go - 2 Plane
description:
TWO GO --
Control both the two plane at the same time.
Avoid the squares on the way.
Fly as far as you can,Have a good time!
VOICE FLY --
Use sound control the plane through squares.
SWING FLY --
Tap control the swing plane to fly as far as you can.

VOICE LEVEL --
24Levels for voice model.
